trans-unit.source: A component that accepts channels and associates them with a service.
trans-unit.target: En komponent som godtar kanaler og tilordner dem til en tjeneste.

trans-unit.source: A ChannelDispatcher object associates an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> at a particular URI (called a listen URI) with an instance of a service.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som du knytter en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>på en bestemt URI (kalt lytte URI) med en forekomst av en tjeneste.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> object can have many ChannelDispatcher objects, each associated with a different listener and listen URI for that service.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>objekt kan ha mange du-objekter, hver knyttet til en annen lytter og lytte URI for tjenesten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: When a message arrives, the ChannelDispatcher queries each of the associated <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher> objects whether the endpoint can accept the message, and passes the message to the one that can.
trans-unit.target: Når en melding ankommer, spørringer du hver av de tilknyttede <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher>objekter om endepunktet godtar meldingen, og sender meldingen til den som can.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher> object is responsible for processing messages from a ChannelDispatcher when the destination address of a message matches the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher.AddressFilter%2A> property and the message action matches the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher.ContractFilter%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher>objektet er ansvarlig for behandling av meldinger fra en du når mål-adressen for en melding som samsvarer med den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher.AddressFilter%2A>egenskapen og meldingen handlingen samsvar i <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher.ContractFilter%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher.ContractFilter%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher.AddressFilter%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher>

trans-unit.source: All properties that control the lifetime and behavior of a channel session are available for inspection or modification on the ChannelDispatcher object.
trans-unit.target: Alle egenskaper som styrer levetid og virkemåten for en økt som kanal er tilgjengelige for inspection eller endringen i du-objektet.

trans-unit.source: In addition to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher>, these include custom <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IChannelInitializer> objects, the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>, the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, the associated and <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg til den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher>, disse omfatter egendefinerte <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IChannelInitializer>objekter i <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>, tilknyttede og <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.IChannelInitializer> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.EndpointDispatcher>
